          <p xml:id="idc07d6732-8980-44cd-919d-21115379686d">(KA, A pk. 41 læg 3; <ref xml:id="idd842fda7-891a-4004-aa9e-905b1d3df052" target="../p305/txt.xml#n305-1" type="journalsAndPapers" n="pap:IIA802-807" rend="Papir 305:1"><hi xml:id="id4d415cb6-de25-4531-8eb7-ad3c15648c43" rendition="#ita">Pap.</hi> II A 802-807</ref>)</p>
